MethodDef.Name: D_DaysInStudy
MethodDef.FormalExpression: Function D_DaysInStudy(ScreenDt, PatientStatus, CompleteDt, DiscontinueDt) If PatientStatus="Fail" then D_DaysInStudy=0 Else Select Case PatientStatus Case "Discontinued" If IsDate(DiscontinueDt) and IsDate(ScreenDt) then D_DaysInStudy = DateDiff("d", ScreenDt, DiscontinueDt) End if Case "Completed" If IsDate(CompleteDt) and IsDate(ScreenDt) then D_DaysInStudy = DateDiff("d", ScreenDt, CompleteDt) End if Case Else If IsDate(ScreenDt) then D_DaysInStudy = DateDiff ("d", ScreenDt, Now) End if End Select End if End Function

MethodDef.Name: Level1DataTypeNotValid
MethodDef.FormalExpression: Function Level1DataTypeNotValid(DataValue, DataType, strFormatRegExpr) If DataValue = "NULL" or DataValue = "" Then Level1DataTypeNotValid = "False" ElseIF LCase(DataType) = "datetime" Then dim objRegExp objRegExp = new RegExp objRegExp.Pattern = strFormatRegExpr objRegExp.IgnoreCase = True dim DateFormatOkay DateFormatOkay = objRegExp.Test(DataValue) objRegExp = nothing Level1DataTypeNotValid = not DateFormatOkay or not IsDate(DataValue) Or Len(DataValue) < 4 ElseIf LCase(DataType) = "float" Then Level1DataTypeNotValid = not isNumeric(DataValue) or InStr(1, DataValue, ",") > 0 or InStr(1, DataValue, "$") > 0 or Right(DataValue, 1) = "-" or Right(DataValue, 1) = "+" or Instr(1, DataValue, "(") > 0 or Instr(1, DataValue, "E") > 0 or Instr(1, DataValue, "e") > 0 ElseIf LCase(DataType) = "integer" Then Level1DataTypeNotValid = not isNumeric(DataValue) or InStr(1, DataValue, ".") > 0 or Right(DataValue, 1) = "-" or InStr(1, DataValue, ",") > 0 or Right(DataValue, 1) = "+" or Instr(1, DataValue, "(") > 0 or Instr(1, DataValue, "E") > 0 or Instr(1, DataValue, "e") > 0 if Level1DataTypeNotValid = False AndAlso isNumeric(DataValue) then Level1DataTypeNotValid = DataValue > 2147483647 or DataValue < -2147483648 end if Else Level1DataTypeNotValid = "False" End If End Function

IF (DataValue >= MinValue) and (DataValue <= MaxValue) THEN Level2RangeNotValid = "False" ELSE Level2RangeNotValid = "True" END IF Else Level2RangeNotValid = "True" END IF Else Level2RangeNotValid = "False" End If End Function
